frames.caption: In a desert landscape, two colossal stone figures stand chained in front of an ancient pyramid. The scene is bathed in warm sunlight, casting long shadows on the sand as small human figures walk below, emphasizing the giants' immense size.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal desert environment with two massive stone statues in chains, positioned before a pyramid. The presence of people walking in the foreground highlights the scale and grandeur of the statues and the ancient setting.
